library(stringr)
setwd("C:/Users/student/Documents/MATH 421")
c2015<- read_excel("c2015.xlsx")
c2015 <- na.omit(c2015)
c2015 <- c2015 %>% filter_all(~!(.=="Unknown"))
c2015 <- c2015 %>% filter_all(~!(.=="Not Rep"))
c2015 <- c2015 %>% filter_all(~!(.==str_detect(.,"Not Rep")))
c2015 <- c2015 %>% filter_all(~!(.==str_detect(.,"Unknown")))
c2015 <- c2015 %>% filter_all(~!(.=="Not Reported"))
c2015$TRAV_SP <- c2015$TRAV_SP %>% str_replace("MPH", "")
c2015$TRAV_SP <- c2015$TRAV_SP %>% str_replace("Stopped", "0")
c2015$AGE <- c2015$AGE %>% str_replace("Less than 1", "0")
c2015$TRAV_SP <- as.numeric(c2015$TRAV_SP)
c2015$AGE <- as.numeric(c2015$AGE)
c2015 <- c2015 %>% filter(SEAT_POS == "Front Seat, Left Side")

c2015 %>% group_by(MONTH) %>% summarize(mean = mean(TRAV_SP)) %>%          mutate(speed_above_below = ifelse(mean > mean(c2015$TRAV_SP),               "above", "below"), standardized_speed = (mean -                      mean(c2015$TRAV_SP))/sd(c2015$TRAV_SP)) %>% 
      ggplot(aes(reorder(MONTH, standardized_speed),                             standardized_speed, label = standardized_speed)) + geom_bar(stat = "identity", aes(fill = speed_above_below),                   width=0.5) +
  labs(title = "Diverging Bars", subtitle = "Normalized Monthly           Average Speed", x="MONTH") + 
  coord_flip()

16

c2015 %>% group_by(INJ_SEV, SEX) %>% summarize(mean = round(mean(TRAV_SP),2)) %>% ggplot(aes(reorder(INJ_SEV, -mean), mean, label=mean)) +
    geom_point(stat="identity", aes(col = SEX), size = 6) +
    geom_text(color = "white", size = 2) +
    labs(title = "Diverging Dot Plot", subtitle = "Average Speed of Injury Type", x= "Injury Severity") +
    coord_flip()

17

c2015 %>% group_by(DAY, SEX) %>% summarize(mean = round(mean(TRAV_SP),2)) %>% mutate(mean1 = ifelse(SEX == "Female", -mean, mean)) %>% 
  ggplot(aes(reorder(DAY,mean1), mean1, fill = SEX))+
  geom_bar(stat="identity", width = 0.6) + scale_y_continuous() +
  coord_flip() +
  scale_y_continuous(breaks= c(seq(-60,60,20)), labels = paste0(as.character(c(seq(60,0,-20),seq(20,60,20))), "mph")) +
  labs(y="Average Speed", x="Day of a month")

c2015 %>% group_by(STATE, MONTH) %>% summarize(mean = round(mean(TRAV_SP),2)) %>% mutate(MONTH1=factor(MONTH, levels=month.name)) %>%  
  ggplot(aes(MONTH1, STATE, fill = mean)) +
  geom_tile(color="white") +
  scale_fill_gradient(low="green", high="red") +   scale_x_discrete(labels = c("Jan", "Feb", "Mar", "Apr", "May", "Jun", "Jul", "Aug", 'Sep', 'Oct', 'Nov', 'Dec'))

c2015 %>% group_by(MONTH, WEATHER) %>% summarize(mean = round(mean(TRAV_SP),2)) %>% mutate(MONTH1=factor(MONTH, levels=month.name)) %>%  mutate(MONTH2 = as.numeric(MONTH1)) %>% 
  ggplot(aes(MONTH2, mean, col = WEATHER)) +
  geom_line() +
  labs(x = "Months", y="Speed") +
  scale_x_continuous(breaks= c(1:12), labels = c("Jan", "Feb", "Mar", "Apr", "May", "Jun", "Jul", "Aug", 'Sep', 'Oct', 'Nov', 'Dec'))
